Package contractAutomata.automaton.label

Class CALabel

  • java.lang.Object
    • contractAutomata.automaton.label.Label
      • contractAutomata.automaton.label.CALabel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Matchable<Label>, Ranked
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CMLabel

    public class CALabel
extends Label
    Class implementing a label of a contract automaton transition. Note: in this class Java Modelling Language contracts have been experimented, only using Extended Static Checker analysis of OpenJML. However, the specs are outdated w.r.t. the current implementation.
    Author:
    Davide Basile
